data.description: Calling All Car Buffs and Mechanics!  Dream 30x40 insulated shop with 14 ft doors, 6” polished/epoxied Slab with rebar and binder, 11,000# Atlas Commercial direct drive/hydraulic lift, Power (220v &110v), Water, and Internet!!  Oh…Did I mention the 3 bed/2bath updated home with its OWN attached 2 car garage?  It boasts skylights, vaulted ceilings, Cozy Woodstove, covered back deck, fenced yard, 5pc primary bath with Jetted tub, New induction/convection range, Laminate floors throughout and a BIG A/C unit for cooler Summers. All on 2.6 square acres with TONS of graveled parking, Chicken coop, and plenty of room for Gardening.  And only a 5 min walk to Beautiful Carney Lake for a Summer full of FUN. See it Today…buy it tomorrow.
